I ordered rare, and um, you got it. Some pink.
Love hanging around here with nature lights, high ceiling and great food too. But what we could do more to save the environment by using less recycle material for our daily life?

Ground floor for salads sandwiches and snacks, while 37th has a sit down restaurant with buffet and take away options including, salads,  western, Indian and a variety of Asian selections. Food is quality, but be careful what you choose. Buffet lunch is good value with diverse options
This connecting floor was continent for taking a break during the day without descending all the long long way to the ground floor. (Unless all you need is cigarette)

reviews.text: Very good place.  For the restaurant semi buffet, it is really cost effective.  😊
I ordered rare, and um, you got it. Some pink.

有幸來到呢頭喫晏(因呢間無晚市)。
位於三十七樓，樓底超高，景觀一流 (席間有鷹近飛盤旋，有點夢幻)。
午餐屬半自助。前菜/甜品多款，食材不錯，味道不俗。
主菜牛扒若係厚切就一流 (算有點可惜) ﹐肉質香嫩無渣。
環境算靜，價位中上。如見客傾生意，算係不錯之選！
食物新鮮，沙拉吧選擇不多但是每樣都好吃
海南雞飯～

reviews.text:
I like to enjoy some simple cafe food and a cup of coffee facing fantastic mountains view through big windows.  The ceiling is high and environment is quiet. Serving simple quick bite  food, wine and bakery. 

Unfortunately, they use disposal utensils which are not user-friendly, in my opinion. Be alert! Weekend will be closed.
Pretty good view and nice location. Easy to get to central. Service is good, facilities are fresh and modern. Five stars recommendation!
Nice environment on the outside. Not a fan of the futuristic elevator and interior design. I just can’t tell where it’s wall and where it’s door
Great companies offering venues as part of CSR.
Nice building and the area near the building is very nice. You can get indian food, cofee and other items nearby.
